        by @{b}Will Harwood@{ub} <147800.97@swansea.ac.uk>

  This is FREEWARE. This little pictures were found in a dank,
  dark corner of my harddrive and I have no idea of where they
  originally came from - hope you don't mind me using them!

  Do you want to easily stick a nice picture into your GUIs? Would
  you like it to remap its palette? Would you like to load it through
  datatypes? Do you mind if it takes ages to load? Would you like
  the option for it to scale? Then dtpic is for you.
	
